<title>USA: Tag 96 proforma ADS $0.83 vs $0.72.</title>
<headline>Tag 96 proforma ADS $0.83 vs $0.72.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>(Expressed in millions of Swiss Francs except for EPS)</p>
<p>  Year Ended		  12/31/96	   12/31/95  Variance</p>
<p> Sales		SFr.419.7	     SFr.379.6	  +10.6%</p>
<p> Gross Profit		     231.8	     205.7     12.7%</p>
<p> Gross Margin		     55.2%	     54.2%</p>
<p> Operating Income		  88.6		76.8     15.4%</p>
<p> Operating Margin		 21.1%	     20.2%</p>
<p> ProForma Net Income (A)	 60.5		52.3     15.7%</p>
<p>ProForma Net Income</p>
<p>  Per Share (A)     SFr.11.24		SFr.9.71	    --</p>
<p>ProForma Net Income</p>
<p>  Per ADS in US $* (A)	US$0.83	   US$0.72	  --</p>
<p> Shares Outstanding	 5,383,721	 5,383,721	  --</p>
<p>Sales for 1996 increased by 10.6% to a record SFr. 419.7</p>
<p>NOTES: Pro Forma figures calculated to adjust for significant changes in capital structure arising from recapitalization, reorganization and initial public offering on September 26, 1996. It provides comparable basis for net income figures assuming the changes in capital structure would have occurred as of January 1, 1995 and excludes foreign exchange impact on US dollar Senior Subordinated Notes.</p>
<p>Full company name is TAG Heuer International SA.</p>
